2.2 Coordinate Frames
The module supports transformations between multiple coordinate systems:

Earth Centered Inertial (ECI) frame - {i}
Earth Centered Earth Fixed (ECEF) frame - {e}
North-East-Down (NED) frame - {n}
Body frame - {b}
Flow frame - {f}

5.3 Usage Example
from mav_simulator.module_sensors import create_sensor

# Create a GPS sensor
gps_config = {
    'type': 'gps',
    'rate': 10.0,  # Hz
    'noise_std': 1.5  # meters
}
gps = create_sensor(gps_config)

# Get sensor reading
vessel_state = {...}  # Current vessel state
gps_reading = gps.measure(vessel_state)



